<plot>From the Academy Award nominated directors of Troublesome Creek, Steven Ascher &amp; Jeanne Jordan, comes a new documentary film,So Much So Fast. A black-humored cliffhanger of romance, guerrilla science and the redefinition of time, So Much So Fast unfolds like a nonfiction novel. Stephen Heywood finds out he has ALS. His brother Jamie becomes obsessed with finding a cure. And the woman who's falling in love with Stephen has a decision to make.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503739</url></doc>
